snippet.title: Palallel - Steam Next Fest Trailer
snippet.description:
Palallel is a cooperative 2D puzzle platformer for two players. You are locked inside a board where you can't see your partner. You'll need to exchange objects and active mechanisms to escape.

Palallel will feature several physics & logic mechanics, more than 100 levels, and a lot of environments.

If you're interested, please wishlist the game on steam and follow us on our socials below !

Discord : https://discord.gg/fXNgBnvRTd
Steam : https://store.steampowered.com/app/1155300/Palallel/
Twitter : https://twitter.com/GoatApeGames
